. Qualification for appointment as chairperson or member of the Council
A person shall be qualified for appointment as chairperson or member of the
Council if that person—
is a citizen of Kenya;
holds a degree from a university recognized in Kenya;
has knowledge and experience of at least ten years, in the case of the
chairperson, or seven years, in the case of a member, in matters relating to any
